Key	Space	A	4	Menu MenuFvwmRoot Nop
Key	Space	A	CM	Menu WindowOptionsMenu Close

# Scroll Desktops
Key	Right	A	CM	GotoDesk	1 0
Key	Left	A	CM	GotoDesk	-1 0

Key 1		A	4 GotoDesk 0 0
